reviewText:
In depth video for beginners!!!
Would recomend to everyone!!!
Easy step by step instructions and more.
All different types of tutus!!!

This is a great tutorial for anyone wanting to make a tutu...either for the first time, or wanting to add the wow factor to the tutu's you already make. I've made basic tutu's in the past, but now I am certain they are going to be amazing.
If you're considering this video, I say go for it. You won't be disappointed. It's a good quality video, easy to follow, and it's a great price for such informative information.

Great DVD. Excellent for learning how to make tutu's and has information beyond the basic tutu.  Very easy to follow. Very happy with my purchase and I recommend to others who enjoy making tutu's and want to try different styles.
